prj.betfair.api.betting.operations

Class OperationBuilder

  • java.lang.Object
    • prj.betfair.api.betting.operations.OperationBuilder

  • public class OperationBuilder
extends java.lang.Object
    This class serves holds a collection of factory methods for the betting operations provided within this API. Each method will return a Builder for the corresponding operation with the preset operation executor provided at creation of the OperationBuilderFactory.
